title: Khilona Bana Khalnayak
subTitle: Tatya Vinchu, a dying gangster, transfer his soul into a doll. The ventriloquist Lakshya unknowingly brings the sinister doll into his life, leading to chaos.

title: Chehre Pe Chehra
subTitle: Dr Wilson, a scientist, develops a theory about humans having an angelic and a demonic side. He conducts an experiment on himself to prove it, but it goes terribly wrong, leading to dire consequences.

title: Jazbaat
subTitle: A woman's life takes an unexpected turn when she joins a dance troupe. However, complications arise when she returns to her village.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Dastaan-E-Rafi
subTitle: Renowned celebrities discuss the life journey of gifted singer Mohammed Rafi, sharing moments and incidents they experienced with him during his career.

title: Kal Aaj Aur Kal
subTitle: Ram Bahadur Kapoor faces a dilemma when his son wants to marry for love, but his father insists on arranging the grandson's marriage.

title: Kirayadar
subTitle: When Anil, son of their absentee landlord, arrives in Mumbai and asks them to move out of his home, Laxmi and Jaya's lives turn chaotic.

title: Naya Daur
subTitle: A man introduces a bus service in an attempt to make quick profits and endangers the peace and livelihood of local farmers and workers.

title: Teesri Aankh
subTitle: Mali brings up an orphan baby boy as her own. Later, when her husband reveals the real identity of the child, she strives to cope with the truth.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Separated at birth, the paths of Shyam, a lousy magician unwittingly roped into a crime, and Toofan, a defender of the people, cross again years later as they reunite to avenge their father.

title: Neela Aakash
subTitle: Neela and Akash fall in love with each other after a comedy of errors. But her drunkard father disapproves of their union as she is the sole breadwinner of their family.

title: Neela Aakash
subTitle: Neela and Akash fall in love with each other after a comedy of errors. But her drunkard father disapproves of their union as she is the sole breadwinner of their family.

title: Ardh Satya
subTitle: Anant, a righteous police officer, is torn between his ethics and dishonest practices in the police department. Soon, he discovers the strong connection between corruption and politics.

title: Painter Babu
subTitle: After an unexpected blow to his father's business, Shyam, who loves Renu, is forced to marry Menaka. Unhappy with the decision, he becomes a rebel and invites more troubles in his life.

title: Bhuvan Shome
subTitle: A lonely bureaucrat goes on holiday to a village in Gujarat where a young peasant woman helps him see beyond his job and develop a newfound empathy for people.

title: Dada
subTitle: Jeetu works as a mechanic, lives in a slum area and is all set to marry Kamini, the girl he loves. But his life is destroyed when he is arrested and convicted for killing Kamini's brother.

title: Heer Ranjha
subTitle: Heer, who belongs to a rich family, and Ranjha, a poor farm boy, fall madly in love with each other. But, their lives take a tragic turn when Heer's parents forcibly marry her off to a wealthy man.

title: Samadhi
subTitle: Lakhan Singh gives up his life of crime when he falls in love and marries Champa. However, things take a turn when she falls sick and he is forced to become a criminal again.

title: Tamacha
subTitle: Raju and Vicky, two childhood friends, reunite after years apart. However, they end up on opposing sides of the law as Raju becomes a crusading officer, while Vicky descends into a life of crime.

title: Tum Haseen Main Jawaan
subTitle: Sunil, a navy officer, falls for Anuradha. However, things get complicated when Ranjeet, Anuradha's admirer, claims that she is a single mother.

title: Kalicharan
subTitle: When Prabhakar, an honest cop, is murdered by Din Dayal, a powerful crime lord, Khanna recruits his doppelganger Kalicharan to defeat Din Dayal.

title: Kalicharan
subTitle: When Prabhakar, an honest cop, is murdered by Din Dayal, a powerful crime lord, Khanna recruits his doppelganger Kalicharan to defeat Din Dayal.

title: Naach Uthe Sansaar
subTitle: A rich man's daughter falls in love with a farmer and wants to marry him. However, her father not only disapproves of this but also humiliates his mother, which makes the farmer seek vengeance.

title: Pyar Kiye Jaa
subTitle: Ramlal, a widower, struggles to find suitable grooms for his daughters and to control his son's film obsession. To make matters worse, one of his former employees launches a protest against him.

title: Jawani Diwani
subTitle: Vijay meets Neeta, the daughter of a Thakur, and falls in love with her. However, things change after he finds out that she has been promised to another man in marriage.

title: Saas Bhi Kabhi Bahu Thi
subTitle: When Sadhana marries Deepak, her manipulative mother urges her to harass her mother-in-law. Subsequently, she also meddles in her son's marriage, turning their lives into a web of misery.

title: Sangam
subTitle: Two best friends, Sundar and Gopal, love the same woman, Radha, while she has feelings only for Gopal. But when Sundar marries Radha, the love triangle is thrown into turmoil.

title: Aakhree Raasta
subTitle: A man is falsely accused of his wife's murder and imprisoned. When he sets out to seek revenge, he finds a police officer on his trail who turns out to be his own son.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Yeh Vaada Raha
subTitle: Vikram, in love with Sunita, faces tragedy when an accident leaves him unaware of her transformation, while Sunita, now under a new identity secretly hopes to rekindle their love.
